{"tid":2415165,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"澳洲國立大學報告：倡設立網站舉報外國干預行為","createTime":"2021-02-20T04:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-20T20:25:59.000Z","uid":39464,"like":31,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"aa057030043457757417faf9c26051ee162a7026","tid":2415165,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:45:08.000Z","msg":"澳洲國立大學發表一份新報告，向政府提出建議，以應對可接受的外國影響活動以及外國干預之間的所謂「灰色地帶」。<br />\n<br />\n報告作者兼國家安全專家曼斯泰德（Katherine Mansted）表示，在 21 世紀，澳洲在處理外國干涉問題上的法律及政策改革，處於全球領先的地位。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「自澳洲聯邦成立以來，澳洲經已有一系列管理外國影響風險的法律，但全球化和數碼化，再加上俄羅斯及中國等現代專制國家的崛起，意味澳洲（應對）外國影響的政策目前急需改變。」<br />\n<br />\n報告建議設立一個獨立專員，並建立一個專門的全國性網站，用以舉報有問題的外國影響行為，並更新關於新聞自由、資訊保護和私隱問題等的法律，以減低有問題外國影響力的風險。<br />\n<br />\n現存的「外國影響透明度登記冊」（Foreign Influence Transparency Register）制度，旨在提供和澳洲政治及重要部門有關的外國影響力的透明度。<br />\n<br />\n但曼斯泰德說：「該登記冊的設計和運作方式，存在一系列問題。」<br />\n<br />\n「結果是，它被認為是一份黑名單，而不是民間社會、企業和政府決策者的有用訊息資源。」<br />\n<br />\n曼斯泰德表示，所有澳洲人在對抗不受歡迎的外國影響上都能發揮其作用，但政府需要做更多工作，令人們能夠在知情的情況下作出適當的抉擇。<br />\n<br />\n她說：「外國影響已從主要『閉門造車』的『精英』做法，轉變為影響社會各個部分的新常態。」<br />\n<br />\n「政府當然有責任，但最終往往要由企業、民間社會團體及普羅大眾，決定什麼形式的影響力是他們可以接受的，並且符合他們的組織和個人價值觀。」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/report-provided-a-roadmap-to-navigate-the-grey-zone-between-foreign-influence-and-interference\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sbs.com.au%2Fchinese%2Fcantonese%2Fzh-hant%2Freport-provided-a-roadmap-to-navigate-the-grey-zone-between-foreign-influence-and-interference&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkmFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=7883a1b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/cantonese/zh-hant/report-provided-a-roadmap-to-navigate-the-grey-zone-between-foreign-influence-and-interference</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://nsc.crawford.anu.edu.au/department-news/18457/navigating-space-between-foreign-influence-and-foreign-interference\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnsc.crawford.anu.edu.au%2Fdepartment-news%2F18457%2Fnavigating-space-between-foreign-influence-and-foreign-interference&d=8a%2F9oMJQTUqWgqWpHd%2BbkmFzq3Uwi%2FWN07E9MureYdc%3D&h=6b33f37c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://nsc.crawford.anu.edu.au/department-news/18457/navigating-space-between-foreign-influence-and-foreign-interference</a>"},{"pid":"5118fd980679c70b4fc8b0d2f311c22d4ac5ecf0","tid":2415165,"uid":70301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"make Australia great again！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c531375f0fe66715f92dd2b9b332e2bf3381aed8","tid":2415165,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:59:05.000Z","msg":"UQ UoA: 我地繼續奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3412603adf43b5e5fbddc4fd8e331606dca0c1a","tid":2415165,"uid":289292,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c531375f0fe66715f92dd2b9b332e2bf3381aed8","tid":2415165,"uid":66324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:59:05.000Z","msg":"UQ UoA: 我地繼續奶 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:28:39.000Z","msg":"8大有邊間唔奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0993550266b4461b006d9db2bbd31a826855e162","tid":2415165,"uid":357710,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5118fd980679c70b4fc8b0d2f311c22d4ac5ecf0","tid":2415165,"uid":70301,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T04:48:11.000Z","msg":"make Australia great again！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2lny/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-20T05:46:13.0